title: Design Solar-Powered Vehicle Architecture
description: Develop the blueprint for an electric vehicle that runs entirely on solar power

title: Develop Solar Panels Integration Design
description: Create a design for integrating solar panels into the vehicle

title: Select and Specify Battery Requirements
description: Research and specify the battery requirements for the solar-powered vehicle

title: Develop Charging Mechanism Design
description: Create a design for the charging mechanism that will store excess solar energy

title: Create Project Roadmap
description: Develop a roadmap for the project, including milestones and key deadlines

title: Research and Select Solar Panel Manufacturer
description: Research various solar panel manufacturers to select the best one for the project

title: Develop Solar Panel Purchase and Integration Plan
description: Create a plan for purchasing solar panels and integrating them into the vehicle design
dependencies: Research and Select Solar Panel Manufacturer
